                           Project 02 - An ALU Chip
                           -----------------------


Submitted Files
---------------
README - This file.
Add16.hdl - Adds two 16-bit binary numbers together
ALU.hdl - Implements a 6-bit control input ALU chip
EqualsZero16.hdl - Determines if a 16-bit chip is equal to zero
FullAdder.hdl - Adds three bits together
HalfAdder.hdl - Adds two bits together
Inc16.hdl - Increments a 16-bit number by 1
Mul.hdl - Performs multiplication on two 16 bit numbers. Truncates output to 16 bits
OneBitMul.hdl - Multiplies a 16 bit input by a single bit
ShiftLeft.hdl - Shifts all bits (other than the MSB) left one bit
ShiftRight.hdl - Shifts all bits (other than the MSB) right one bit
Xor16.hdl - Xors two 16-bit numbers together two (one from each input number) bits at a time

Remarks
-------
